data.description: Beautiful and unique 3 bedroom 2 full bath home right in the heart of Winston Salem. The public library is right next door within walking distance and shopping is just minutes away. Huge great room with fireplace and don't forget to check out fascinating closet under the stairs. Come on by and see this beautiful home and bring an offer!
